rows.label: qst720401_msg0001
rows.name: Ivan, is that you?

rows.label: qst720401_msg0002
rows.name: Whoa!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0003
rows.name: L-Adel-sama!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0004
rows.name:
Please... A moment...
Garck!! Hngh!!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0005
rows.name: Urgh?! Grhhhhgh...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0006
rows.name: Hey! He's turning blue!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0007
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Throat...jammed!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0008
rows.name: Here! Drink some water!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0009
rows.name: *Gulp gulp gulp...*

rows.label: qst720401_msg0010
rows.name: Aaah...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0011
rows.name: Phew...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0012
rows.name: Looks like your color's returned...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm afraid I have no idea who you are...
But I owe you my life!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0014
rows.name:
Ah... I think you're exaggerating a little
there...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0015
rows.name:
Not at all! I'd give you something by
way of thanks, but I'm afraid it's a
difficult time for me right now.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0016
rows.name:
Ivan! Have you been snitching food
on the sly again?

rows.label: qst720401_msg0017
rows.name:
Adel-sama... Uhm... No!
Perish the very thought!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0018
rows.name:
So what were you doing here then?
Because whatever it was, it sounded
awfully like someone guzzling to me...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0019
rows.name:
Prince! ...I was...disposing of spoiled
food, Your Highness!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0020
rows.name:
You mean...you were scarfing down
rotten food?! That can't be good for
your health!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0021
rows.name:
Thank you kindly for your concern.
But I am fortunate to have a naturally
robust gut.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0022
rows.name:
I couldn't risk giving this inferior stuff
to the resistance fighters.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0023
rows.name: That...sorta makes sense?

rows.label: qst720401_msg0024
rows.name:
You could say I was maximizing
efficiency by combining food quality
management with disposal.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0025
rows.name:
And if I can quieten the rumblings of
my stomach at the same time... Well,
that's a tertiary bonus.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0026
rows.name:
Yes, Ivan, I get it. You'll stop at
nothing to make things more efficient.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0027
rows.name:
As we've just seen, you'll even risk
your own life for it!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0028
rows.name:
Could you give me a report on the
state of our food supplies?

rows.label: qst720401_msg0029
rows.name: Of course!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0030
rows.name:
Well, since Your Highness's recent
return, we've been catering for a few
more soldiers.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0031
rows.name:
We've organized food-gathering squads
and dispatched them here and there,
but sadly manpower does not suffice.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0032
rows.name:
I suppose I bear some responsibility
for that.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0033
rows.name:
Yeah... We should help out with
the catering, too.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0034
rows.name:
Indeed. We must do what we can to
improve the situation until His Majesty
returns.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0035
rows.name: Thank you all! You're too kind!

rows.label: qst720401_msg0036
rows.name:
Here's the list of our most needed
foodstuffs.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0037
rows.name:
Two Grimdark Crabs,
four portions of Feris Beastmeat...

rows.label: qst720401_msg0038
rows.name:
Two large Lactonuts, and six
measures of Weeping Flour...
That seems easily doable.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0039
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]We should probably get one more
of each than he asked for...
He's pilfer-prone.

rows.label: qst720401_msg0040
rows.name:
I guess we have everything we need to
start searching!
